query:
INSERT INTO codigosAcessoGestante (gestanteId, codigo, destino, expiraEm, createdAt)
SELECT 
  id,
  LPAD(FLOOR(RAND() * 1000000), 6, '0') as codigo,
  'teste@gestantesapp.com',
  DATE_ADD(NOW(), INTERVAL 15 MINUTE),
  NOW()
FROM gestantes 
WHERE email = 'teste@gestantesapp.com'
LIMIT 1;

SELECT codigo, expiraEm, 'VÁLIDO POR 15 MINUTOS' as status
FROM codigosAcessoGestante 
WHERE destino = 'teste@gestantesapp.com' 
ORDER BY createdAt DESC 
LIMIT 1;
